WEBVTT

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:01.936
Kada vas odbiju u životu,

00:15:01.960 --> 00:15:04.176
kada ste suočeni s novom preprekom

00:15:04.200 --> 00:15:06.216
ili novim neuspehom,

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:08.056
razmotrite mogućnosti.

00:15:08.080 --> 00:15:09.296
Ne bežite.

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:10.536
Ako ih samo prigrlite,

00:15:10.560 --> 00:15:12.640
mogle bi da postanu takođe vaši darovi.

00:15:13.160 --> 00:15:14.376
Hvala vam.

00:15:14.400 --> 00:15:17.814
(Aplauz)